Detailed Description

template<class PtrType = TeleoReactor *>
struct TREX::transaction::details::reactor_id_traits< PtrType >

ID traits for TeleoReactor.

Gives a way to acces to the name of a reactor in order to store them in a TREX::utils::list_set
